OL,3,CGerry Adams was 'de facto leader' of
OL,4,CIRA, court told
OL,6,FGerry Adams was the "de facto leader"
OL,7,Fof the IRA, a police intelligence
OL,8,Fofficer has told the High Court.
OL,10,FGiving evidence for the civil trial
OL,11,Fagainst the former Sinn Fein
OL,12,Fpresident, witness B, who cannot be
OL,13,Fnamed, said he concluded that Mr Adams
OL,14,Fwas "undoubtedly a member of the Army
OL,15,FCouncil".
OL,26,@nD@UOUnD@eO]vD@EOUwD@HO]
OL,1,W~k4 jw=hw1 hw}h7}j7}            G1/14
