OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F448A1773346284
OL,3,CGerry Adams was 'de facto leader' of
OL,4,CIRA, court told
OL,6,FThe case has been brought by victims
OL,7,Fof three bombings in England: Jonathan
OL,8,FGanesh, who was injured in the 1996
OL,9,FLondon Docklands bombing; John Clark,
OL,10,Fa victim of the 1973 Old Bailey
OL,11,Fbombing in London; and Barry Laycock,
OL,12,Fa victim of the 1996 Arndale shopping
OL,13,Fcentre bombing in Manchester.
OL,15,FThe three men allege that Mr Adams was
OL,16,Fa leading member of the Provisional
OL,17,FIRA on those dates, including of its
OL,18,FArmy Council, and are seeking #1 in
OL,19,Fdamages.
OL,1,W~k4 jw=hw1 hw}h7}j7}            G2/14
OL,2,W/*% /*%/"-$+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
