FL,449,440,140,120,000,100
PN,44803
SC,0003
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F448A1773346284
OL,3,CGerry Adams was 'de facto leader' of
OL,4,CIRA, court told
OL,6,FMr Adams denies ever being in the
OL,7,FProvisional IRA and is defending the
OL,8,Fclaim.
OL,10,FIn a statement for the trial on
OL,11,FThursday, witness B said: "A great
OL,12,Fdeal of intelligence which I read
OL,13,Fcommunicated, both explicitly and
OL,14,Fimplicitly, that Adams was a senior
OL,15,Fmember of the IRA Army Council and the
OL,16,Fde facto leader of the IRA."
OL,26,@sD@[OUxD@\O]
OL,1,W~k4 jw=hw1 hw}h7}j7}            G3/14
OL,2,W/*% /*%/"-$+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
