OL,3,CGerry Adams was 'de facto leader' of
OL,4,CIRA, court told
OL,6,FA handful of protesters surrounded Mr
OL,7,FAdams' car as he arrived at the High
OL,8,FCourt on Thursday, shouting and
OL,9,Fholding placards.
OL,11,FIn court, witness B sat behind a
OL,12,Fscreen while being cross-examined.
OL,14,FJames Robottom, for Mr Adams, said it
OL,15,Fwas previously a criminal offence to
OL,16,Fbe an IRA member.
OL,18,FHe said there is "no evidence" Mr
OL,19,FAdams was arrested for a criminal
OL,20,Foffence until the 21st century.
OL,26,@zD@ROUzD@^O]
OL,1,W~k4 jw=hw1 hw}h7}j7}            G5/14
OL,2,W/*% /*%/"-$+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
