PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F448A1773346284
OL,3,CGerry Adams was 'de facto leader' of
OL,4,CIRA, court told
OL,6,FWitness B replied: "I would say he was
OL,7,Fconsistently being looked at to see if
OL,8,Fthere was any evidence that would meet
OL,9,Fthe criminal burden of proof."
OL,11,FHe also said that "very few people"
OL,12,Fwere prosecuted for membership of the
OL,13,FIRA and that it was usually "added on
OL,14,Fif someone was caught red-handed with
OL,15,Fguns or bombs".
OL,26,@nD@TOUqD@^O]sD@SOUsD@cO]uD@]OUwD@NO]
OL,1,W~k4 jw=hw1 hw}h7}j7}            G6/14
