CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F448A1773346284
OL,3,CGerry Adams was 'de facto leader' of
OL,4,CIRA, court told
OL,6,FMr Robottom also put to the witness
OL,7,Fthat Mr Adams was one of the people
OL,8,Fpushing hardest for peace in the 1990s.
OL,10,FWitness B said: "Our assessment is not
OL,11,Fsimply because he wanted peace, but
OL,12,Fbecause he knew his organisation was
OL,13,Fgoing nowhere and he wanted to extract
OL,14,Fthe best possible price.
OL,16,F"He was the one truly strategic leader
OL,17,Fthey had. He is a strategic thinker,
OL,18,Fthat's why he is where he is today."
OL,26,@rD@QOUxD@AOUzD@dO]
OL,1,W~k4 jw=hw1 hw}h7}j7}            G8/14
