PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F448A1773346284
OL,3,CGerry Adams was 'de facto leader' of
OL,4,CIRA, court told
OL,6,FEdward Craven KC, for Mr Adams, said
OL,7,Fat the start of the trial on Monday
OL,8,Fthat the former Sinn Fein president
OL,9,F"emphatically, unequivocally and
OL,10,Fcategorically denies that he was ever
OL,11,Fa member of the IRA".
OL,13,FHe also said there was "no shortage of
OL,14,Fpeople with an axe to grind" who
OL,15,Fsought to discredit his client.
OL,26,@qD@AOUsD@TO]uD@XOUvD@\O]
OL,1,W~k4 jw=hw1 hw}h7}j7}            G9/14
