PN,44810
SC,0010
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F448A1773346284
OL,3,CGerry Adams was 'de facto leader' of
OL,4,CIRA, court told
OL,6,FPeople such as British officials,
OL,7,Fmembers of the Royal Ulster
OL,8,FConstabulary or other republicans
OL,9,Fopposed to the peace process had an
OL,10,Finterest in discrediting Mr Adams, the
OL,11,Fbarrister added.
OL,13,FIn written submissions, Mr Craven
OL,14,Fsaid: "The defendant's alleged factual
OL,15,Fand legal responsibility for the
OL,16,Fclaimants' injuries is strongly
OL,17,Fcontested, as is the claimants'
OL,18,Fability to bring these claims against
OL,19,Fthe defendant several decades after
OL,20,Fthe expiry of the applicable
OL,21,Flimitation period."
OL,26,@vD@GOU}D@SO]
OL,1,W~k4 jw=hw1 hw}h7}j7}           G10/14
