PN,44812
SC,0012
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F448A1773346284
OL,3,CGerry Adams was 'de facto leader' of
OL,4,CIRA, court told
OL,6,FMr Hanley replied: "Ultimately, we
OL,7,Fhave got a finite resource and finite
OL,8,Fpeople and it is a matter of
OL,9,Fpriorities."
OL,11,FHe added: "The threat facing us at
OL,12,Fthat time was feuding between
OL,13,Floyalists and sectarian murders and
OL,14,Fthis emerging threat from dissident
OL,15,Fgroups.
OL,17,F"After a while it gets, not left on
OL,18,Fthe shelf, but regarded as not that
OL,19,Fimportant."
OL,26,@nD@TOUqD@LO]sD@KOUyD@AOU{D@KO]
OL,1,W~k4 jw=hw1 hw}h7}j7}           G12/14
OL,2,W/*% /*%/"-$+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
