OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F448A1773346284
OL,3,CGerry Adams was 'de facto leader' of
OL,4,CIRA, court told
OL,6,FMr Craven asked: "Are you saying that
OL,7,Fif someone is going to make a no-
OL,8,Fcomment interview you don't bother
OL,9,Farresting them?"
OL,11,FThe retired officer said: "No, but
OL,12,Fthere were priorities."
OL,14,FThe trial, before Mr Justice Swift, is
OL,15,Fdue to conclude next week.
